Text:
I can't believe no one has mentioned this yet, but I've quickly listened to both "Big Sean - Dance" and "Justin Bieber - As Long As You Love Me" and they are both highly distorted during some parts...

Also the album art for Big Sean - Dance is... edited. Like someone literally took their face and pasted it over Big Sean's face in MS Paint.
I take that back. ALL the album art is fucked up.

"David Guetta - Turn Me On" is also distorted.

I would pass on this torrent.
The .m3u and .pls files included don't work either.
